journey
  title Grant Application Experience (Extended)
  
  section Preparation
    Identify call & fit assessment           : 4 : applicant, grant office
    Build consortium / partner outreach      : 3 : applicant, partners
    Eligibility check (institution + PI)     : 5 : grant office
    Read guidelines & evaluation criteria    : 4 : applicant
    Create timeline & responsibilities (RACI): 4 : applicant, grant office
    Collect templates (CVs, biosketch, ethics): 3 : applicant, admin
    Internal go/no-go decision               : 2 : applicant, management

  section Concept & Scoping
    Define objectives & impact narrative     : 3 : applicant
    Align with call priorities               : 4 : applicant, grant office
    Draft work packages & milestones         : 3 : applicant, partners
    Risk register & mitigation plan          : 3 : applicant, grant office
    Data management plan (DMP) outline       : 2 : applicant, data steward
    Ethics/self-assessment (if relevant)     : 2 : applicant, compliance

  section Budgeting & Compliance
    Build budget & justification             : 2 : applicant, finance
    Validate eligible costs                  : 3 : finance, grant office
    Secure letters of support                : 3 : applicant, partners
    Finalize subcontracting / procurement    : 2 : applicant, procurement
    Internal compliance review               : 3 : grant office, compliance
    Obtain institutional approvals           : 2 : management, grant office

  section Writing & Iteration
    Draft proposal (v1)                      : 2 : applicant
    Internal scientific review               : 3 : reviewers, applicant
    Integrate feedback (v2)                  : 2 : applicant
    Edit for clarity & consistency           : 3 : grant office
    Final partner contributions received     : 1 : partners
    Final proofread & formatting             : 2 : applicant, grant office

  section Submission
    Create portal workspace                  : 3 : applicant, grant office
    Upload documents & validate forms        : 2 : applicant
    Run portal validation checks             : 3 : applicant
    Fix validation errors                    : 1 : applicant
    Submit                                   : 1 : applicant
    Receive submission confirmation           : 5 : applicant, grant office

  section Review & Outcome
    Administrative eligibility screening     : 3 : funder
    External peer review                     : 2 : funder, reviewers
    Panel evaluation / ranking               : 2 : funder
    Wait for feedback                         : 1 : applicant
    Receive decision                          : 5 : applicant, grant office

  section Post-decision
    If awarded: grant agreement negotiation  : 3 : applicant, grant office, funder
    If awarded: kickoff & project setup      : 4 : applicant, finance
    If rejected: debrief & resubmission plan : 3 : applicant, grant office
